{"tid":1466402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做錯又點？唔割，大家一齊諗點補飛。","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:04:13.000Z","uid":134134,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cfaaef80a6f6337325ab31065db9f8a8660804b7","tid":1466402,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"所有宣傳、文宣、交談<span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理</span>，不否認，不辨論。<br />\n再俾人問，話條友有同一件衫同打現場手足，同關荃灣斬人事，再spin過去黑警問題。<br />\n繼續煲大五大訴求，黑警殺人。<br />\n再有現場手足俾人訪問，記住你唔係開記者會，唔需要交代任何嘢，輕輕講兩句，記住<span style=\"color: red;\">我無嘢講</span>。<br />\n講多錯多，記得be a drop of water。"},{"pid":"2d9b35b9bfcbcf6bef484290ab71b0eab618dee7","tid":1466402,"uid":134134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:14.000Z","msg":"鬼一定捉唔哂，一齊諗點做靚佢。"},{"pid":"2b39ec1f91fa623bbafa15a7c2f7c0d514be4ba2","tid":1466402,"uid":230511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">團結團結團結</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個係唯一有希望贏嘅關鍵<br />\n已經係得1%勝率㗎啦<br />\n唔好再輕率魯莽<br />\n再入機場係仲有機會反勝<br />\n大家主動去搵遊客道歉等佢地體諒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做公關比外媒睇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記住，不分化不割蓆，唔好未開戰先自亂軍心"},{"pid":"ae719bd0d65af0f621691ed75a1949035dc35280","tid":1466402,"uid":134134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:44.000Z","msg":"點解咁多街坊撐我哋？就係我哋做得太靚，而狗做得太柒，民意係要理。"},{"pid":"c157a5bd3872c7044bde7b58171d205d9ff65171","tid":1466402,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:10.000Z","msg":"［文宣煲大佢］有疑似黑社會入機場踩線搞恐襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1465124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1465124</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地已經冇可能再割蓆"},{"pid":"93e78c47bc3b15ccf648531aae93093a8e010baf","tid":1466402,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:20.000Z","msg":"